## 3. Pack promotion dependency graph

Wave placement is the current dependency-ordering proxy (see `.specify/pack-l5-promotion.ttl`'s
`l5p:PromotionWave` individuals) until a finer per-pack `l5p:dependsOn` edge set is authored.
Packs in an earlier wave are promotion prerequisites for packs in a later wave that reuse their
vocabulary or generated surface.

{% for w in waves -%}
