## 4. Shared promotion machinery map

Wave 2 ("Reusable Level 5 promotion machinery") is the explicit charter for this artifact —
see the wave-2 entry in section 3 above. Populated as machinery is actually extracted and
proven reusable across ≥2 packs, not speculatively.

## 5. Promotion-wave plan

See section 3 (dependency graph) — the 9 waves ARE the plan, ordered `l5p:order` "1".."9".

