| {{ p.id }} | {{ caps_for_pack | map(attribute="capName") | join(sep=", ") }} | {{ p.obligation }} |
{% endfor %}

## 7. Consumer-replacement ledger

Capability 12 ("Consumer replacement") status per pack is tracked via the missing-capabilities
column above (§6) — a pack with cap12 absent from its missing list has a proven
delete-and-regenerate consumer path; see `.specify/pack-l5-promotion.ttl`'s per-pack
`l5p:missingCap` triples for the authoritative source.

